## File permission

### To check the permission
  
  - $ ls -l
  
  $ls -l /home/tom
-rwxr-xr--  1 xxx   users 1024  Nov 2 00:10  xxx-file
drwxr-xr--- 1 yyy   users 1024  Nov 2 00:10  tomdir

### To change the permission
  - $chmod o+wx tom
  
  $chmod o+wx,u-x,g = rx testfile
  
  ### change ownership
  - $ chown user filelist
  
  
